    Takes the raw string from the TCP buffer and splits it up into a map of dataref:valueArray.

    This singleton is the reference to the data handler object.
    DataObserverPacket  
    DisconnectAll
    Unsubscribes datarefs from Xplane and resets the socket.
    ReceiveData
    This class is our TCP receiver.
    SendData
    Sends data strings to ExPlane plugin via TCP using existing socket.

    SubscribeDatarefs
    Subscribes to all the datarefs in he database.
    UnsubscribeDatarefs
    Unsubscribes from all the datarefs.
